  33  # Default port is 8001. 
  34  # 
  35  # Integers are sent as 32 bits signed, network byte order. 
  36  # Strings are sent as their length (as integer), then data (UTF-8 
  37  # encoded). The length is computed after encoding. 
  38  # Dates are sent as strings, formatted YYYY-MM-DD. 
  39  # 
  40  # The exact workflow for both desktop and device is documented as Dia 
  41  # diagrams, in the "Design" subdirectory of the iPhone sources. 
  42
